Actually in russia you don't have to wait for the movie to premier to get a cam copy. All theaters get the movie a week before it is premiered. In some cases 2 days. during special screenings, lets just say for employees , some dude with a hefty wallet comes and gets a cam copy which he sells to distributors who make 1000s of dvds to market for 3 to 4 $ a pop.
